  "texts": [
    "Gemini (https://gemini.google.com/), previously known as Google Bard, is a versatile language AI that utilizes Bidirectional Encoder Representations from Transformers (BERT).",
    "This advanced model enables researchers to generate text, visualize content, receive writing assistance, translate materials, and provide accurate and comprehensive responses to queries.",
    "The advanced AI using the latest Ultra 1.0 model can manage intricate tasks such as coding, logical reasoning, and collaborative creative projects effectively.",
    "12 Gemini has three additional advanced prototypes Gemini pro (GPro), Gemini nano (GNano), and Gemini ultra (GUltra).",
    "Among them GPro is a sophisticated AI model created to comprehend and produce human language, facilitating interaction through both short exchanges and extended conversations, with capabilities extending to understanding and generating code, text summarization, content creation, formatting and editing."
  ],
